# AI Resume Analyzer 🤖

An AI-powered full-stack application that analyzes resumes against job descriptions using LLM APIs and generates tailored interview insights.

## 🚀 Features

- Resume PDF Parsing
- AI Resume Matching
- Skill Gap Analysis
- AI-Generated Interview Questions
- Authentication System
- PDF Report Generation
- Responsive Dashboard

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB Atlas
- Mongoose
- JWT Authentication

### AI & Utilities
- Gemini / OpenAI API
- PDF Parsing
- REST APIs

---

## ⚡ AI Features

- Resume scoring
- Keyword extraction
- Skill matching
- Tailored interview question generation
- ATS-style resume evaluation

